<!--
  Notification small icon for the hourly task alarm (and any future notifee
  notification). Android renders the small icon using ONLY the alpha channel,
  so it MUST be a white silhouette on a transparent background — a full-colour
  image (e.g. @mipmap/ic_launcher) would be masked to a solid white square.

  Referenced by name "ic_notification" in mobile/src/services/notifications.ts.
  Before this file existed the name resolved to nothing, notifee built the
  notification with no small icon, and Android silently rejected it at fire
  time — so the alarm was scheduled but never actually rang. See that file.

  Glyph: a simple clock face, matching an "hourly alarm".
-->
